######################################
###       2. Plot Shape Files      ###
######################################

# plot shape file 
ggplot() + 
  geom_sf(data = aoi_boundary_HARV, 
          size = 1, 
          color = "black", 
          fill = "#3B3131") + 
  ggtitle("Polygon extent Plot") + 
  coord_sf()
